âœ” **IAM Groups simplify permission management** by grouping users with similar access needs.  
âœ” **Users inherit all policies** assigned to the group.  
âœ” **Best Practice:** Assign policies to groups instead of individual users.  
âœ” **Common Groups:** Admins, Developers, Support, Billing, S3-Read-Only, etc.  
âœ” **AWS CLI can be used** to automate group management.  

